# Force LF line endings for text sources and fixtures regardless of the
# checking-out platform's core.autocrlf setting. Without this, a Windows
# checkout (Git's default core.autocrlf=true there) converts LF to CRLF on
# checkout for anything it detects as text — confirmed to break
# src/core/rightsize-fixture.txt's exact-content round-trip assertion in
# mountable-file.test.ts on the msb-windows CI job (fixture read back as
# "...fixture\r\n" instead of the committed "...fixture\n").
* text=auto eol=lf
